name: Mackenzie Global Sustainable Dividend Index ETF
longDescription: The ETF seeks to replicate, to the extent reasonably possible. The Fund before fees and expenses, the performance of the Solactive Developed Markets Sustainable Dividend Select Index, or any successor thereto. It invests primarily in equity securities with above-average and stable dividend yield in developed markets.
